><p data-block-id=\"e53056c4-5e78-4685-9d39-02c9fa8420b2\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"d4fc461e-77d4-4e93-b6a4-95652e301b57\">แสดงชื่อร้านค้า</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"b4f8a664-8a7f-4f0b-ab84-3300e08a00a1\">XENDIT</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"260ee695-3783-478d-b6ce-168812cf5235\">แสดงชื่อผู้ใช้</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"3f6d647e-1833-437d-9371-94b019551449\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"ebe59eaf-3581-4b5e-9133-086846171bc3\">กำหนดวันหมดอายุ</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"69cfa81b-5b12-4684-a3d3-8cb4231eef2f\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"7750e331-7b15-4423-9ba5-f771994775fe\">เวลาในการชำระบัญชี (ชั่วโมง)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"4f6f26f7-78ce-4ee2-86ca-e0e91c209e24\">T+2 BUSINESS DAYS</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"6779fc15-6426-43e4-83b0-b2e6307dba73\">การคืนเงิน</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"e763223f-2dbe-41be-84b3-3f5eb0ddb4d4\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"0baabc7e-a92b-49d0-af45-796c16289f04\">การคืนเงินบางส่วน</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"8d7ea2ae-48b1-4f75-a0c5-f0ad349be77d\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"166f9598-76a9-48a7-b24b-9c06b9f896ce\">การคืนเงินบางส่วนหลายครั้ง</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"caa96435-1191-4058-9ebc-afd3a21a945a\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"256467fa-b7fd-45f2-b88e-195088282404\">ระยะเวลาการคืนเงิน (วัน)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"4f7f6f8a-2e73-4aa5-8176-f3341285afc1\">N/A</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"5c93e485-a74d-4a50-8a1b-9bba2a9f420b\">การผสานรวมที่เข้ากันได้</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"637ff717-8b2b-4064-8310-d9c57c754e25\">Payment API</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"2b081c08-ffd2-493a-b253-c4931f5f1c75\">วิธีการชำระเงิน</h2><ol data-block-id=\"7d99ad68-e560-4694-8e5e-5aace1ffb55e\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"fcdd7171-436b-4481-a75d-b1ca8510cef6\"><p data-block-id=\"72545818-c18b-4e6f-a493-1f8f83e7e6a5\">ไปที่สาขา CVM pawnshop ที่ใกล้ที่สุดก่อนรหัสชำระเงินจะหมดอายุ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"4e1d5fc1-c71e-4fd2-99a3-6a62970879b2\"><p data-block-id=\"f3b42f26-0ed5-46da-b12c-71ac5af9327a\">แจ้งพนักงาน/เจ้าหน้าที่แคชเชียร์ว่าคุณต้องการชำระเงินผ่าน Dragonpay Payment</p></li><li data-block-id=\"8dc8811b-8e9d-4a37-8f38-bbdc6c6f7af2\"><p data-block-id=\"f4ff179b-fc93-4b18-bad4-c7a50a8e462f\">คุณจะถูกขอให้เขียนรายละเอียดต่อไปนี้ลงบนกระดาษ:</p><ol data-block-id=\"b2ee998a-c99e-4a26-9297-871134de94f8\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"da0bc416-4aa3-47bc-8f83-2c70ed10789a\"><p data-block-id=\"e0c810c4-bed1-417a-bd49-b27f4009ca3f\">ชื่อของคุณ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"a50f731b-4940-449c-8ef8-e94e75576a7b\"><p data-block-id=\"cd7ce936-ed55-43bb-9b1f-84bb9dea21de\">หมายเลขโทรศัพท์มือถือของคุณ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"a4119b46-cfca-43f0-a0d1-f3890282ff9d\"><p data-block-id=\"9d581cc2-369c-493e-9b14-831a0bec3638\">วันเกิดของคุณ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"9efd745a-2b90-40ce-811a-0ab98a682d3b\"><p data-block-id=\"83f779aa-eed6-4c02-ab3d-01fc455107c1\">รหัสชำระเงินที่ร้านค้าให้มา</p></li><li data-block-id=\"3f1fe4c9-e053-4bf1-ab5d-4201c15a2774\"><p data-block-id=\"d68abcd7-2abb-4a3a-9129-5e26145f0564\">จำนวนเงิน</p></li><li data-block-id=\"52dcf67c-03b9-4fa9-b2f5-218a4dd89d4e\"><p data-block-id=\"be2d0b18-e68f-4ec4-86e4-4fd757e32f65\">วัตถุประสงค์ในการชำระเงิน</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"67127e7b-41aa-4724-8c08-727d8498f2a7\"><p data-block-id=\"196802d1-6d53-44aa-831f-4709cfc36225\">ยื่นกระดาษที่กรอกแล้วพร้อมกับการชำระเงินของคุณ (เงินสดเท่านั้น) ให้กับพนักงาน/เจ้าหน้าที่แคชเชียร์</p></li><li data-block-id=\"846ed916-1c1a-4ea0-b1d5-8c908dad3646\"><p data-block-id=\"aebc9379-337d-48c1-820a-119afd96a756\">คุณจะได้รับใบเสร็จรับเงินเป็นหลักฐานการชำระเงิน<br type=\"inline\"><img data-block-id=\"9600be3e-c91f-47ea-86a8-8a8593ebb598\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Screenshot 2025-01-05 at 09.47.30.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"415\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"center\" datadisplay=\"inline\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:415px;\"></p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"8e9aac87-b7ff-4f0e-b9c9-0178d8f76e42\"></p><p data-block-id=\"1fba7422-3f0f-475f-a3cd-ed72e33bce4f\"></p><p data-block-id=\"acd97665-43b1-498b-89ca-e66b24c0a68f\"></p><p data-block-id=\"490a489a-2a58-4dc9-96ea-9e5cc09fc8be\"></p>","SeoTitle":"CVM","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"CVM","Slug":"cvm","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"0ea65c3d-a38c-40be-a208-d546ab91ccec\"><img data-block-id=\"ddc1ed3e-11cd-4537-bffb-fa882bb16eac\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/CVM Pawnshop Home.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt title=\"image(23).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"40d09386-139f-4cf1-8307-2c85d716974e\">CVM Pawnshop, con su extensa red de sucursales en Filipinas, permite a los comercios (businesses) aceptar pagos (payments) en ventanilla de clientes (customers) que prefieren transacciones fuera de línea. Los clientes (Customers) pueden liquidar (settle) compras en línea proporcionando un número de referencia de transacción (transaction reference number) en cualquier sucursal de CVM, lo que lo convierte en una opción conveniente para aquellos sin cuentas bancarias o que prefieren pagos (payments) en efectivo.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">Características</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"735\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:735px;width:735px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:463px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"db4dfef8-c563-4305-8c29-ef2b1aa63d40\">Código de Canal</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"e1e6e1e6-c602-409f-9e71-21f3f2b349df\"><code>CVM</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"05742465-0957-4c43-b4a1-a714d1ec5bd9\">Moneda</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"3f8936e1-14e1-4482-860e-cd08d70c3f38\">PHP</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"216547ce-9149-4c98-863b-af7a9b417559\">Monto Mínimo</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"17190da0-2088-4c47-9f9a-c92fafebdd48\">50.00</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"917595fc-cd1e-4638-a3ac-8c763018c400\">Monto Máximo</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"2760134e-54b9-4aaa-9d81-734957700cdf\">30,000.00</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"dd693bd7-6fa5-470c-a762-3bd25581ee55\">Flujo de Aprobación del Usuario</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"171da64c-8dad-441b-8a44-dc494f51d517\">PRESENT TO CUSTOMER</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"00b142a2-96d8-469f-a603-d7f653f2f6a6\">Código de Pago Reutilizable</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"c221f08c-7f47-4f90-8365-ce103ec676ed\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"a15e3b11-bb7c-4496-bbdd-cbc61b5faf78\">Código de Pago Personalizado</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"e53056c4-5e78-4685-9d39-02c9fa8420b2\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"d4fc461e-77d4-4e93-b6a4-95652e301b57\">Mostrar Nombre del Comercio</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"b4f8a664-8a7f-4f0b-ab84-3300e08a00a1\">XENDIT</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"260ee695-3783-478d-b6ce-168812cf5235\">Mostrar Nombre del Usuario</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"3f6d647e-1833-437d-9371-94b019551449\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"ebe59eaf-3581-4b5e-9133-086846171bc3\">Establecer Expiración</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"69cfa81b-5b12-4684-a3d3-8cb4231eef2f\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"7750e331-7b15-4423-9ba5-f771994775fe\">Tiempo de Liquidación (horas)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"4f6f26f7-78ce-4ee2-86ca-e0e91c209e24\">T+2 BUSINESS DAYS</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"6779fc15-6426-43e4-83b0-b2e6307dba73\">Reembolso</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"e763223f-2dbe-41be-84b3-3f5eb0ddb4d4\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"0baabc7e-a92b-49d0-af45-796c16289f04\">Reembolso Parcial</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"8d7ea2ae-48b1-4f75-a0c5-f0ad349be77d\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"166f9598-76a9-48a7-b24b-9c06b9f896ce\">Reembolso Parcial Múltiple</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"caa96435-1191-4058-9ebc-afd3a21a945a\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"256467fa-b7fd-45f2-b88e-195088282404\">Validez del Reembolso (días)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"4f7f6f8a-2e73-4aa5-8176-f3341285afc1\">N/A</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"5c93e485-a74d-4a50-8a1b-9bba2a9f420b\">Integración Compatible</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"637ff717-8b2b-4064-8310-d9c57c754e25\">Payment API</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"2b081c08-ffd2-493a-b253-c4931f5f1c75\">Cómo pagar</h2><ol data-block-id=\"7d99ad68-e560-4694-8e5e-5aace1ffb55e\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"fcdd7171-436b-4481-a75d-b1ca8510cef6\"><p data-block-id=\"72545818-c18b-4e6f-a493-1f8f83e7e6a5\">Visite la sucursal de CVM Pawnshop más cercana antes de que el código de pago (payment code) expire.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"4e1d5fc1-c71e-4fd2-99a3-6a62970879b2\"><p data-block-id=\"f3b42f26-0ed5-46da-b12c-71ac5af9327a\">Indíquele al cajero/personal que realizará un Pago (Payment) de Dragonpay.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"8dc8811b-8e9d-4a37-8f38-bbdc6c6f7af2\"><p data-block-id=\"f4ff179b-fc93-4b18-bad4-c7a50a8e462f\">Se le pedirá que escriba en una hoja de papel los siguientes detalles:</p><ol data-block-id=\"b2ee998a-c99e-4a26-9297-871134de94f8\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"da0bc416-4aa3-47bc-8f83-2c70ed10789a\"><p data-block-id=\"e0c810c4-bed1-417a-bd49-b27f4009ca3f\">Su Nombre</p></li><li data-block-id=\"a50f731b-4940-449c-8ef8-e94e75576a7b\"><p data-block-id=\"cd7ce936-ed55-43bb-9b1f-84bb9dea21de\">Su Número de Teléfono Móvil</p></li><li data-block-id=\"a4119b46-cfca-43f0-a0d1-f3890282ff9d\"><p data-block-id=\"9d581cc2-369c-493e-9b14-831a0bec3638\">Su Fecha de Nacimiento</p></li><li data-block-id=\"9efd745a-2b90-40ce-811a-0ab98a682d3b\"><p data-block-id=\"83f779aa-eed6-4c02-ab3d-01fc455107c1\">Código de Pago (Payment Code) proporcionado por el Comercio (Merchant)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"3f1fe4c9-e053-4bf1-ab5d-4201c15a2774\"><p data-block-id=\"d68abcd7-2abb-4a3a-9129-5e26145f0564\">Monto</p></li><li data-block-id=\"52dcf67c-03b9-4fa9-b2f5-218a4dd89d4e\"><p data-block-id=\"be2d0b18-e68f-4ec4-86e4-4fd757e32f65\">Propósito del Pago (Payment)</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"67127e7b-41aa-4724-8c08-727d8498f2a7\"><p data-block-id=\"196802d1-6d53-44aa-831f-4709cfc36225\">Entregue el papel llenado al cajero/personal junto con su pago (solo efectivo)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"846ed916-1c1a-4ea0-b1d5-8c908dad3646\"><p data-block-id=\"aebc9379-337d-48c1-820a-119afd96a756\">Recibirá un recibo como comprobante de pago (payment)<br type=\"inline\"><img data-block-id=\"9600be3e-c91f-47ea-86a8-8a8593ebb598\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Screenshot 2025-01-05 at 09.47.30.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"415\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"center\" datadisplay=\"inline\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:415px;\"></p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"8e9aac87-b7ff-4f0e-b9c9-0178d8f76e42\"></p><p data-block-id=\"1fba7422-3f0f-475f-a3cd-ed72e33bce4f\"></p><p data-block-id=\"acd97665-43b1-498b-89ca-e66b24c0a68f\"></p><p data-block-id=\"490a489a-2a58-4dc9-96ea-9e5cc09fc8be\"></p>","SeoTitle":"CVM","Description":null}]